    "Profit motives and lack of transparency can pose a challenge for research.",
    "For example, it is unclear to what extent OpenAI, the company behind ChatGPT, retains the data provided by users.",
    "For this reason, it is of utmost importance to ensure that data given to LLMs is anonymized and pre-selected in a way that guarantees no harm to any research participants should that data be accessed by a non-authorized party.",
    "Sensitive and/or traceable data that is not manifestly public is at risk in the event of a security breach at OpenAI.",
    "Researchers need to take account of these issues when undergoing ethics review, and as they carry out the research."
